songs.lyrics:
[Verse 1]
Yeah I’ve been searching far and wide
To try to find something worth my time
And you’re so nice,
Yeah you’re so nice to me

[Verse 2]
Yeah I’ve been searching far and wide
To try to find something worth my time
And I’m so dead inside, I cry
But it’s alright
Yeah, it’s alright

[Verse 3]
I’ve been searching far and wide
To try to figure out my mind
And I’m quite stumped
Yeah I’m quite stumped tonight
songs.title: Far & Wide
